title: GOVERNOR Caitlyn Jenner?! Well, Actually ...
description:
Governor Caitlyn Jenner? Hey, stranger things have happened. We also take a deep dive into the D.C. statehood nonsense. Mask “guidelines” are doing more harm than good. And there is a rise in hate crimes against Asians, but not a lot of media attention. Why do you think that is? #CaitlynJenner​ #DCstatehood​ #StopAsianHate​
